Correa also referred to the new medical treatment of Venezuelan President Hugo Chavez in Cuba.
I have just discussed with Venezuelan Vice-President Nicolas Maduro and he told me that routine medical treatment is already planned and that he is waiting for the end of the campaign to return to Cuba.
"This does not mean a relapse of President Chavez's state of health," he commented.
